                        <interp inst="t18451027-name-877" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES WAY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am shopman to Mr. Mears—I saw the prisoner run<lb></lb>ning and followed him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
