                        <interp inst="t18451027-name-878" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN NIXON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable K</hi> 380.) I took the prisoner—he said nothing.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was standing against the butcher's shop, talking to two little boys who sell rings; they went and stood by the picture-shop, and about half-past eight o'clock there was a cry of "Stop thief!" I ran after them, and this man laid hold of me.</p>
